DOC.brief_summary: To compare the pharmacokinetic characteristic of LBEC0101 25mg with the active comparator, Enbrel® 25 mg.
DOC.brief_title: Study to Compare the Safety and Pharmacokinetic Characteristics of LBEC0101 25 mg With Those of Enbrel®
DOC.criteria: Healthy males, 20 to 45 years of age the moment of screening Body mass index is between 18.0 and 30.0 kg/m The tuberculosis patient or latent tuberculosis patient Hypersensitivity response to the test and comparator drugs
